credits.title: Credits
credits.credits:
This program contains emojiflags library from [GitHub, jonathan-kosgei](https://github.com/jonathan-kosgei/emoji-flags).

Huge thanks to Rapptz for creating **rewrite** version of discord.py.
This uses:
discord.py@rewrite, mw-api-client, emoji, github3.py, requests, beautifulsoup4, pypinyin.
scratchapi2 is made by the owner, apple502j.
Two emoji, specifically mute and deafen emoji, is based on Twemoji [1f3a7](https://github.com/twitter/twemoji/blob/gh-pages/svg/1f3a7.svg) and [1f3a4](https://github.com/twitter/twemoji/blob/gh-pages/svg/1f3a4.svg).
